gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Wizards 112, Raptors 109
gameRecap.excerpt: Washington defeats Toronto, 112-109. For Washington, Deni Advija led the way with 22 points, 13 rebounds, and five assists while Jordan Poole added 18 points, 12 assists, three steals in the win. Gary Trent Jr. finished with 31 points, four rebounds, and three steals with Kelly Olynyk tallying 14 points, six rebounds, 10 assists, and two steals for Toronto in the losing effort. Washington wins and improves to 13-58, while Toronto moves to 23-48 in the loss.
